Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.44,JapaneseText,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.4\4a&HFF&}Hola, jovencita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.90,JapaneseText,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\c&H000000&}Me llamo Rudeus.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.90,JapaneseText,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.4\4a&HFF&}Me llamo Rudeus.
